      "date": "2012-02-04 08:50:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: (17 inline comments)\n\nI haven't looked through the whole patch yet, it's very large.\n\nIdeally, this patch would start out by just copying files from lustre/obdfilter and committing those with the new names, so that Git can link the files in its commit history, and then additional patches modify the obdfilter code to become OFD.\n\nThe other benefit of doing it this way is that it avoids losing code changes that were made to obdfilter since the time that OFD was forked several years ago.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
